Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:16.00,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(40,270)\b1\fad(1000,1000)\bord0\shad0\fs26}{\fn方正雅士黑 简}{\c&HE5E5E5&\K200}钢 琴 家\N{\fs12\fax-0.5\b0}{\fnTimes New Roman\K200}The Pianist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是席皮尔曼先生吗  -你好\N{\rEng}- Mr. Szpilman? - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是特地来拜访您的  我很喜欢您的演奏\N{\rEng}I came specially to meet you.I love your playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位?\N{\rEng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫多萝塔 我是裘瑞克的妹妹\N{\rEng}My name's Dorota, I am Jurek's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您流血了\N{\rEng}You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\rEng}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 多萝塔\N{\rEng}Come Dorota
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过些时日你大可写爱慕信给他 但现在时机不对\N{\rEng}You can write him a fan letter later.This isn't the best time. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘瑞克 你以前把她藏在哪里?\N{\rEng}Jurek, where have you been hiding her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不知道要带什么 -你老是带太多东西\N{\rEng}- I don't know what to take. - You always take too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要带几只提箱?\N{\rEng}How many suitcases are you taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢 我要带上西蒙叔父的肖像画吗?\N{\rEng}What do you think, should I take uncle Szymon's portrait?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带不带随便你 你自己决定\N{\rEng}Take it, don't take it,take what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我急出病来了吗?\N{\rEng}Can't you see I'm worried sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就要回家了 他会没事的\N{\rEng}He'll come home, he'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有另一只和这个一样的箱子...\N{\rEng}You should have another case just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 瓦列迪克回家了\N{\rEng}Mama, Wladek is home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢老天 瓦列迪克\N{\rEng}Thank God. Wladek!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你受伤了吗? -一点小伤 不要紧的\N{\rEng}- You're wounded? - No, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都忧虑成疾了\N{\rEng}I've been worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过她不用担心 你要随身带着证件\N{\rEng}I told her not to worry.You had your papers on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你被炸到的话 他们就晓得该把你送到那里去\N{\rEng}If you'd been hit by a bomb,they'd know where to take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨瑞 别...别说那种话 愿上帝宽恕你\N{\rEng}Henryk, don't say things like that.God forbid. God forbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 瓦列迪克回来了\N{\rEng}Papa, Wladek is home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么跟你说的? 你在做什么?\N{\rEng}What did I tell you? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有谁看见我的宽边帽?\N{\rEng}Is anybody see my hat with the wide brim?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在进行轰炸 广播关闭了\N{\rEng}They've bombed us. We're off the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华沙不是唯一的广播站\N{\rEng}Warsaw is not the only radio station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收拾行李 亲爱的 把你的东西打包好\N{\rEng}Pack, darling.Get your things packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要到哪里去?\N{\rEng}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-离开华沙 -离开华沙去哪里?\N{\rEng}- Out of Warsaw. - Out of Warsaw where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说吗?\N{\rEng}You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说什么?\N{\rEng}Heard what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没看见报纸吗?\N{\rEng}Haven't you seen the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rEng}No
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报纸在哪里?\N{\rEng}Where's the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿来包东西了\N{\rEng}I used it for packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她把报纸拿来包东西 -政府已经迁到陆柏林了\N{\rEng}- She used it for packing. - The government has moved to Lublin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以四肢健全的男人都必须离开这座城市\N{\rEng}22All able-body men must leave the city, go across the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了建立一道新的防御线\N{\rEng}set up a new line of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了女人 没人还留在这栋房子里\N{\rEng}There isn't anybody left to the building, only the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人都已经离开了\N{\rEng}The men have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人去建立新防御线 你打算做什么?\N{\rEng}What do you think you'll do while they set up a new line of defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拖着你的箱子到处游荡吗?\N{\rEng}Wonder around with your suitcases?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收拾一下 瓦列 没时间了\N{\rEng}Pack, Wladek. There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里都不去\N{\rEng}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我也不要离开\N{\rEng}Good. I'm not going anywhere either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡闹了 我们必需在一起\N{\rEng}Don't be ridiculous,we've got to keep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 如果要死的话 \N{\rEng}Look. If I'm going to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿死在自己家里 我不走\N{\rEng}I prefer to die in my own home, staying put.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝宽恕你\N{\rEng}God forbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了 电台有重要消息 听\N{\rEng}Shut up, I've got something. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...据BBC报导\N{\rEng}...from the BBC in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英国政府尚未得到任何...\N{\rEng}The British government having received no reply...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对德国政府发出的最后通牒的回复\N{\rEng}to the observations presented to the German government...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式向纳粹德国宣战\N{\rEng}has declared war on nazi Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-太棒了 太棒了 -预计...\N{\rEng}- That's wonderful! Wonderful! - It is expected that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...在数小时内\N{\rEng}...within the next few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法国将发布同样的声明\N{\rEng}France will make a similar declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波兰将不再孤立无援\N{\rEng}Poland is no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 太棒了\N{\rEng}Wonderful, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 这真是一顿美妙的晚餐\N{\rEng}Mama, that was a great dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEng}It certainly was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每当有值得庆贺的事情 你需在饭菜上花心思\N{\rEng}When there's something to celebrate,you've got to make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为大不列颠和法国举杯\N{\rEng}Here's to Great Britain and France!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就说吧? 我没告诉你吗?\N{\rEng}I told you? Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会没事\N{\rEng}All will be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5,003块\N{\rEng}Five thousand and three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部就这些吗?\N{\rEng}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5,003波币 我们就剩下这些了\N{\rEng}Five thousand and three zlotys, all we've got left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还超出3,003元\N{\rEng}It's 3,003 zlotys too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 最新流动资产限额条例\N{\rEng}Look."Further restrictions regarding liquid assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹太人在家中放置现金上限为2,000波币\N{\rEng}Jews will be allowed to keep a maximum of 2,000 zlotys at home. "
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其余的钱该怎么处理呢?\N{\rEng}What do we do with the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它存进银行里 帐户会被冻结\N{\rEng}Deposit it in a bank. a blocked account.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银行 谁会笨到把钱存进德国人的银行里?\N{\rEng}Banks! Who'd be stupid enough to deposit money in a German bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以把钱藏起来\N{\rEng}We could hide the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这里 我们可以把钱藏在花盆下面\N{\rEng}Look here.We can hide the money under the flowerpots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们要采取通过通过实践考验的办法\N{\rEng}no no no, I'll tell you what we'll do.We'll use tried and tested methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们上一次是怎么做的吗?\N{\rEng}You know what we did in the last war?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在桌脚凿了个洞 把钱藏进去\N{\rEng}We made a hole in the table leg,and hid the money in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果他们把桌子扛走呢?\N{\rEng}and suppose they take the table away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子扛走是什么意思?\N{\rEng}What do you mean take the table away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人会闯进犹太人家里夺取任何他们想要的东西\N{\rEng}the Germans go into Jewish homes and they just take anything they want
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家俱 值钱的物品 任何东西 \N{\rEng}furniture, valuables, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会吗?\N{\rEng}Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 他们怎可能会要这样一张桌子?\N{\rEng}idiot, Why'd they want to take a table like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么?\N{\rEng}What on earth are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\N{\rEng}Listen. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最理想的地方 \N{\rEng}This is the best place for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会想到要搜查花盆\N{\rEng}No-one would think of looking under the flowerpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不  听我说 我已经想过了...\N{\rEng}No, listen. I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是吗? 这想法倒与众不同 -我们该怎么做?\N{\rEng}- Really? That's a change. - You know what we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要运用心理学\N{\rEng}We use psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运用什么?\N{\rEng}We use what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把钱和表放在桌上\N{\rEng}We leave the money and the watch on the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后像这样把它们遮住\N{\rEng}and we cover them like this. In full view.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜吗?\N{\rEng}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人会到处搜索别的地方 \N{\rEng}The Germans will search high and low and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证他们不会发现这个\N{\rEng} I promised that they never notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我见过最愚蠢的事情\N{\rEng}That's the stupidest thing I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们当然会发现 瞧着\N{\rEng}Of course they'll notice. Look.Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜\N{\rEng}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我是傻瓜\N{\rEng}And you call me stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那方法很好 那是最不容易被...\N{\rEng}that's very good. because that's the last place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这得花多长时间把钱塞进去啊\N{\rEng}This would take hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们又不赶时间 -那用不了多久\N{\rEng}- We're not in a hurry. - It won't take hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 那你要怎么把钱拿出来\N{\rEng}How will you get them out? Tell me that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-一张张扯出来吗? -听我说\N{\rEng}- You reach them out individually. - No-one listens to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静 拜托有点秩序\N{\rEng}Quiet, order, order, please
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是律师 她喜欢秩序\N{\rEng}The lawyer, she likes order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\rEng}Listen, just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把表放在花盆下\N{\rEng}Look.The watch we put under the flowerpot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后把钱塞进小提琴里\N{\rEng}and the money we stuff in the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我还能弹奏吗?\N{\rEng}But I'll still be able to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 会有办法的\N{\rEng}You'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘瑞克 我是瓦列 席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Jurek? It's Wladek Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗?\N{\rEng}Wladek, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很好 谢谢 你呢?\N{\rEng}fine, We're fine, thank you.And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种局势下还算不错\N{\rEng}Fine, under the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你为什么打电话 \N{\rEng}I guess I know why you're calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们实在无能为力...\N{\rEng}There's nothing we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电台不会恢复\N{\rEng}They won't reopen the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我知道 但是裘瑞克...\N{\rEng}Yes, I know, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有音乐 没有波兰人听的广播 什么都没有 \N{\rEng}No music, nothing,no radios for the Polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我确信像你这样的钢琴家\N{\rEng}But sure you'll find work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会找到工作的\N{\rEng}A pianist like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧 但是...\N{\rEng}Maybe, maybe not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我无意冒犯 但我...\N{\rEng}listen,don't be offended,but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我打电话来不是为了讨论我以后的工作\N{\rEng}didn't call to discuss my future carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对裘瑞克唠叨了好几个礼拜\N{\rEng}I nagged Jurek for weeks and weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后他投降了 说  \N{\rEng}and at last he gave in and said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"好吧 明天和我一起去电台"\N{\rEng}"All right, come with me tomorrow",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我来了 但他们把电台炸毁了\N{\rEng}so I came and...they bombed the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能与你那样认识很不错\N{\rEng}Meeting you like that was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的吗? -是的 这...让人记忆深刻\N{\rEng}- Really? - Yes, it was unforgettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很喜欢您的演奏 席皮尔曼先生\N{\rEng}I alwys love your playing, Mr. Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我瓦列\N{\rEng}Call me Wladek, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能像你这样演奏萧邦的曲目\N{\rEng}No-one plays Chopin like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望那是个赞美\N{\rEng}I hope it's a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然是这个意思\N{\rEng}Of course, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...开个玩笑\N{\rEng}I was... trying to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿意跟我去帕拉迪索喝杯咖啡吗?\N{\rEng}Should we go Pradiso and have a coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐意之至\N{\rEng}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 你是做什么的?\N{\rEng}And you, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚从音乐学校毕业\N{\rEng}I finished with the conservatoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是乐师?\N{\rEng}You're a musician?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只是...\N{\rEng}Yes. But only just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪样乐器? 抱歉 哪样乐器?\N{\rEng}What instrument? I'am sorry,What instrument?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大提琴\N{\rEng}The cello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢看女士演奏大提琴\N{\rEng}I love to see women playing the cello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁止犹太人进入\N{\rEng}JEWS FORBIDDEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是无礼 他们怎能这样?\N{\rEng}This is disgraceful.How dare they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人就是这样 他们比希特勒还希特勒\N{\rEng}You know what people are like, they want to be better nazis than Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要去抗议 -算了\N{\rEng}- I'm going in there to complain. - No
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要 相信我\N{\rEng}It's better not, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对你来说太屈辱了\N{\rEng}It's so humiliating. Someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去别处吧\N{\rEng}find somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以到公园散步\N{\rEng}We can walk in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行 官方有令 犹太人禁止进入公园\N{\rEng}No, we can't.Official decree.No Jews allowed in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 你是开玩笑吗?\N{\rEng}My God. Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有开玩笑 是真的\N{\rEng}I'm not joking, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们可以坐在长椅上\N{\rEng}I suggest we could sit in a bench,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但官方另有禁令 "犹太人禁止坐在公共长椅上"\N{\rEng}but another official decree "no Jews allowed on public benches".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真是荒谬\N{\rEng}This is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你我们可以做什么吧 我们只能站在这里交谈\N{\rEng}I tell what we can do,We can just stand here and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想这是被允许的 不是吗?\N{\rEng}and I think we're allowed to do that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你拉大提琴的 多萝塔 好极了\N{\rEng}So, you play the cello. Dorota, That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最欣赏的作曲家是谁?\N{\rEng}And who's your favorite composer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萧邦? 是吗? 那...\N{\rEng}Chopin? Really? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得学他的大提琴奏鸣曲 不是吗?\N{\rEng}you'll have to learn to play his cello sonata, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你呢 瓦列?\N{\rEng}What about you, Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我可以为你伴奏 我弹钢琴 你拉大提琴\N{\rEng}Perhaps I could accompany.Me on the piano, you on the cello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席皮尔曼先生 你真是太棒太棒了\N{\rEng}Mr. Szpilman, you're quite,quite wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我瓦列\N{\rEng}Call me Wladek, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华沙特区的犹太人 需配带标志\N{\rEng}"Free emblems for Jews in the Warsaw district.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在此下令 华沙特区所有的犹太人...\N{\rEng}I hereby order that all Jews in the Warsaw district...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出门需配带醒目的标志\N{\rEng}will wear visible emblems when out of doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此令自1939年12月1日起强制执行\N{\rEng}This decree will come into force on the first of December, 1939...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,适用于12岁以上的犹太人\N{\rEng}and applies to all Jews over 12 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,标志需配带于右臂...\N{\rEng}The emblem will be worn on the right sleeve...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在白底绣上一颗蓝色的大卫王之星\N{\rEng}and will represent the blue star of David on a white background.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,底布必需要够大...\N{\rEng}The background must be sufficiently large...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为星星的顶点间距离要8厘米\N{\rEng}for the star to measure eight centimeters from point to point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线条的宽度必需为1厘米\N{\rEng}The width of the arms of the star must be one centimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未遵从此令的犹太人将受严厉惩罚\N{\rEng}The Jews that do not respect this decree will be severely punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华沙特区首长\N{\rEng}Governor of the Warsaw district,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费沙博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Fischer. "
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会戴\N{\rEng}I won't wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会戴 我不要被贴上标签\N{\rEng}I won't wear it.I'm not going to be branded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看\N{\rEng}Let me see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是否意味着我们得自行准备这些臂章\N{\rEng}Does it say that we have to provid these armbands ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们上哪里去找?\N{\rEng}Where will we get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用去找 我们不会戴\N{\rEng}we won't to get them. We're not going to wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么没有鞠躬?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原凉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不准走人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走水沟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这个了吗?\N{\rEng}Have you seen this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 我正在工作 什么事儿?\N{\rEng}What? What? I'm working. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他们将要安置我们的地方\N{\rEng}It's where they're going to put us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说"安置我们"是什么意思?\N{\rEng}What do you mean "put us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"华沙特区首长 费沙博士...\N{\rEng}"By order of the governor of the Warsaw district, Dr. Fischer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于在华沙建立犹太人隔离区的命令\N{\rEng}concerning the establishment of the Jewish district in Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹太人隔离区即将建成 所有犹太人...\N{\rEng}There'll be created a Jewish district in which all Jews
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华沙本地人或外地人 都必需进驻"\N{\rEng}living in Warsaw or moving to Warsa will have to reside. "
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这里\N{\rEng}Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"居住在指定区之外的犹太人...\N{\rEng}"Jews living outside of the prescribed area...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必需在1940年10月31日前迁至隔离区"\N{\rEng}will have to move to the Jewish district by 31 of October, 1940."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里不可能把我们全部装下\N{\rEng}They won't get all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里太小了 华沙有40万犹太人\N{\rEng}It's too small.There's 400 thousand of us in Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 36万人 这样便有可能\N{\rEng}No, 360 thousand.So it will be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办?\N{\rEng}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我现在该怎么办\N{\rEng}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈?\N{\rEng}Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 这是什么?\N{\rEng}Mama, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20波币\N{\rEng}20 zlotys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就剩下这些了 20波币\N{\rEng}That's all we have left, 20 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20波币可以拿来买什么?\N{\rEng}What can I buy with 20 zlotys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了一直吃马铃薯 马铃薯 马铃薯\N{\rEng}I'm sick of cooking potatoes,potatoes, potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这个价格 这是我的出价\N{\rEng}That's the price.That's what I'm offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你接受 没人会出更高的价\N{\rEng}My advice is to accept.You won't get more from anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李帕先生 但这可是贝西斯坦牌的\N{\rEng}it's a Bechstein! Mr.Lipa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,000元...我建议你收下吧\N{\rEng}2 thousand. My advice is to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你饿肚子的时候怎么办? 啃钢琴吗?\N{\rEng}What are you going to do when you're hungry? Eat the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-滚出去 你这龌龊卑鄙的家伙 -你是怎么回事?\N{\rEng}- Get out! - What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们宁愿把它丢掉 滚\N{\rEng}We'd rather give it away. go on,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天还没吃过东西吧?\N{\rEng}Haven't you eaten today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在挣扎什么?\N{\rEng}What are you suffering from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是疯狂\N{\rEng}You people are crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在帮你 2千元 而且运费由我来付\N{\rEng}I'm doing you a favor. Two thousand and I'm paying for the removal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至不算运费\N{\rEng}I'm not even charging for the removal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天还没有吃东西\N{\rEng}You haven't eaten today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了\N{\rEng}You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿走吧\N{\rEng}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.76,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\b1\pos(192,200)\bord0\blur1.2\fad(300,300)\fscx85\fsp0.5}1940年10月31日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多萝塔\N{\rEng}Dorota
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\rEng}Hello. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原本没有要来\N{\rEng}I didn't want to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看见这一幕\N{\rEng}I didn't want to see all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我...我控制不了自己 \N{\rEng}but...I couldn't stop myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你近来好吗?\N{\rEng}How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不尽然\N{\rEng}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我表哥被逮捕了\N{\rEng}They arrested my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘瑞克说他们会释放他的\N{\rEng}Jurek says they'll let him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不幸\N{\rEng}This is disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会太久的 别担心\N{\rEng}It won't last long. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对自己也是这么说的\N{\rEng}That's what I said myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太荒谬了\N{\rEng}It's too absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我该走了\N{\rEng}I... I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期...\N{\rEng}Well, I'll see you...soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见\N{\rEng}Good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说实话\N{\rEng}Well...to tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为情况会更糟\N{\rEng}I thought it would be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要睡在哪里?\N{\rEng}Where will we sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和女孩儿们睡厨房\N{\rEng}I sleep in the kitchen with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和亨瑞还有爸爸睡这里\N{\rEng}You, Henryk and papa, in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\rEng}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来看啊\N{\rEng}Come and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开\N{\rEng}Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开 走开\N{\rEng}Go away! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\rEng}Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖出什么了吗?\N{\rEng}Sell anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就卖出一本杜思妥也夫斯基的"白痴"\N{\rEng}just one,Dostoyevsky's "Idiot"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3元波币\N{\rEng}3 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过比昨天好\N{\rEng}Better than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3枚肮脏的波币\N{\rEng}Three lousy zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有人却大把大把的赚钞票\N{\rEng}And there are people there making millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才不知道呢\N{\rEng}You don't know, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们贿赂警卫 警卫于是睁一只眼闭一只眼\N{\rEng}They bribe the guards,the guards turn a blind eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们大量输入食物 烟酒 法国化妆品\N{\rEng}They bring cartloads of food,tobacco, liquor, French cosmetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穷人在他们周围死去 他们连痰也没啐一口\N{\rEng}And the poor are dying all around and they don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请问你看见我丈夫伊沙克 沙曼了吗?\N{\rEng}Excuse me, have you seen my husband, Izaak Szerman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个高大英俊的男人 他蓄着灰色的胡子\N{\rEng}A tall handsome man,with a little gray beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有吗? -恐怕没有\N{\rEng}- No? - I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 祝好梦\N{\rEng}Good-bye.Sleep well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果看见他 请写信给我好吗?\N{\rEng}But if you see him, write to me, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊沙克 沙曼\N{\rEng}Izaak Szerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得要有一条非犹太人的街道穿过我们的地方?\N{\rEng}Why do we have to have a gentile street running through our area?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们不绕过去?\N{\rEng}Why can't they go around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:19:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 他们就要建一座桥了 你没听说吗?\N{\rEng}Don't worry about it. They're about to build a bridge. Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一座桥? 一个笑话\N{\rEng}A bridge! A bridge!Those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人声称他们智商高\N{\rEng}The Germans claim to be intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我怎么想吗? 他们根本是不折不扣的白痴\N{\rEng}But do you know what I think?I think they're totally stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有家人要养\N{\rEng}I have a family to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却得在这里花上半辈子时间等他们放行\N{\rEng}I spend half of my time here...waiting for them to let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们以为我来这里干嘛 来听音乐的吗?\N{\rEng}Maybe they think I come here to listen to the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-说什么呢 你很急? -你有意见?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-找点乐子 -对 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞 跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 来  跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去跟他一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪开 空出地方让这些犹太佬跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别停
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续跳 跳快点 继续 犹太佬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续跳 跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们回来了\N{\rEng}Good, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶兹札克 海勒正在等你们\N{\rEng}Itzak Heller has been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有什么事吗? -坐下来 请喝茶\N{\rEng}- What's this about? - Sit down, have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等姑娘们回来我再开饭\N{\rEng}I'll start lunch when the girls get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来这干什么?\N{\rEng}So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他带饼干来\N{\rEng}He brought cakes, he is up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爸爸做珠宝生意回来 他干得不错 是吧\N{\rEng}His father is back in the jewellery business,doing well him.eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人惊奇 珠宝\N{\rEng}Amazing, jewellery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在招人\N{\rEng}We're recruiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在招人?\N{\rEng}Who is recruiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别耍小聪明 我是以朋友的身份来这里\N{\rEng}Don't be clever with me. I'm coming as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全国各地的犹太人涌进城市\N{\rEng}They're bringing Jews in from all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快隔离区会有50万人 \N{\rEng}Soon there will be half million people in the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要更多的犹太人警察\N{\rEng}We need more Jewish police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更多的犹太人警察\N{\rEng}More Jewish police!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我用警棍打那些反抗盖世太保的犹太人?\N{\rEng}you mean you want me to beat up Jews in my truncheon and catch the Gestapo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要有人做这件事 亨瑞\N{\rEng}Someone has got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么是我?\N{\rEng}But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你只征召富家子弟\N{\rEng}I thought you only recruited boys with rich fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看我父亲 看看我们 我的意思是...\N{\rEng}Look at my father, look at us...I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我在看 这就是为什么我在这里\N{\rEng}I'm looking at you, that's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们全家可以过好一点的生活\N{\rEng}Your whole family can have a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要继续靠卖书维持生存 苟延残喘吗?\N{\rEng}You want to struggling survive for selling the books in the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此\N{\rEng}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在帮你们\N{\rEng}I'm doing you people a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你呢 瓦列?\N{\rEng}What about you,Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是位了不起的钢琴家 而我们有很棒的警察爵士乐团\N{\rEng}You're a great pianist. We've got a police jazz band.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会展开双臂欢迎你加入我们 加入我们吧\N{\rEng}They'd welcome you with open arms. Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有工作\N{\rEng}You've got no work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我有工作\N{\rEng}Thank you, I've got work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 当然\N{\rEng}right, yes it is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瓦列 他想要你停一下\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, Wladek. he wants you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁要我停?\N{\rEng}Who wants me to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是说 看好的那边面\N{\rEng}I always say, look on the bright side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.88,0:24:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小小的隔离区里 你是知识份子 专业人士\N{\rEng}You're in a small ghetto with intellectuals, professional people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比我们都更优秀\N{\rEng}You're better off than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这巨大的隔离区是个烂泥坑\N{\rEng}Here in the large ghetto it's a cesspool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱哈达 给我点事情做吧\N{\rEng}You have to give me something to done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是位艺术家 鼓舞人们的灵魂\N{\rEng}You're an artist Wladek, you keep peoples' spirits up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做得够多了\N{\rEng}You do enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想帮忙 我想做点什么\N{\rEng}I want to help, I want to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.30,0:24:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太出名了 伙计\N{\rEng}You're too well known.buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.23,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗?\N{\rEng}you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们音乐家不是优秀的谋略者\N{\rEng}You musicians don't make good conspirators.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太...太音乐了\N{\rEng}You're too... too musical.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.62,0:24:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他是谁? -辛契 梅耶克\N{\rEng}- Who is that? - Symche Majorek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.12,0:24:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传单满天飞 这城市要清除不受欢迎的人\N{\rEng}There are notices going up. City is to be cleansed of the undesirables.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.52,0:24:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-总是有传单满天飞 -你好 辛契\N{\rEng}- There's always notices going up. - Hello, Symche.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.59,0:24:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 多列克 您好 吉丝凯女士\N{\rEng}Dyrek. Mrs. Ysken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘哈达 工作忙吗?\N{\rEng}Jehuda, working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.50,0:24:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅耶克 这位是波兰最伟大的钢琴家\N{\rEng}Majorek, This is the greatest pianist in Poland.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.60,0:24:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许也是全世界最棒的\N{\rEng}Maybe the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.97,0:24:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列迪斯洛 席皮尔曼 见见梅耶克\N{\rEng}Wladyslaw Szpilman, meet Majorek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.11,0:25:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好 -久仰大名\N{\rEng}- How do you do? - I know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.94,0:25:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但未曾听过您演奏\N{\rEng}I've never heard you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.35,0:25:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅耶克一直都在军中 是个出色的男人\N{\rEng}Majorek used to be in the Army.Brilliant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.42,0:25:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一与他捍格的是 他不是个社会主义者\N{\rEng}The only thing I've got against him is he's not a socialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.35,0:25:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好现在离开 瓦列 宵禁时间快到了\N{\rEng}You better go now, Wladek. It's nearly curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.69,0:25:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们印了几份报纸吗?\N{\rEng}You know how many copies we print of our newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500份\N{\rEng}Five hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.93,0:25:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道一份报纸平均有几个人传阅吗??\N{\rEng}You know how many people on average read one copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.87,0:25:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20人\N{\rEng}Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.70,0:25:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总共有一万名读者\N{\rEng}That makes 10 thousand readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.50,0:25:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些将为反动催生\N{\rEng}This will start the uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.47,0:25:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅耶克把它们藏进内裤 然后留在厕所里\N{\rEng}Majorek hides them in his underpants and leaves them in toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厕所?\N{\rEng}Toilets?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.61,0:25:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有我找得到的厕所\N{\rEng}As many toilets as I can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.81,0:25:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人绝不会使用犹太人的厕所\N{\rEng}Germans never use Jewish toilets.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.45,0:25:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他们而言太干净了嘛\N{\rEng}They're too clean for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.99,0:25:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 拜托 帮帮我 先生\N{\rEng}Please, mister, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.44,0:26:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑 你个小杂种\N{\rEng}Hold it! You little bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.20,0:26:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住 站住\N{\rEng}Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.10,0:26:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住\N{\rEng}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.10,0:26:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 快  快来\N{\rEng}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.34,0:26:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊 男孩\N{\rEng}Come on, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.11,0:26:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 站起来 站起来\N{\rEng}Stand up! Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.55,0:26:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 站起来\N{\rEng}Stand up! Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.15,0:27:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 就今晚这一次 别谈论任何不好的事情\N{\rEng}Please, tonight for once, I don't want anything bad talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.75,0:27:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好享用这一餐\N{\rEng}Enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.18,0:27:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么我来说件有趣的事\N{\rEng}fine,Then I'll tell you something funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.59,0:27:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道罗席嘉医生吗?\N{\rEng}You know who I mean by Dr. Raszeja?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.22,0:27:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那位军医? -对 军医\N{\rEng}- The surgeon? - The surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.99,0:27:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别问我为什么 但因为某个原因\N{\rEng}for some reason and not ask me why
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.13,0:27:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人允许他到犹太人区做手术\N{\rEng}The Germans allowed him into the ghetto to perform an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.93,0:27:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为犹太人?\N{\rEng}On a Jew?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.13,0:27:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让波兰人为犹太人开刀?\N{\rEng}They let a Pole to come in to operate on a Jew?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.20,0:27:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿到了通行证 我就知道这些 所以...\N{\rEng}He got a pass, that's all I know. Anyway, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.84,0:27:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他让病人昏睡过去然后开始动手术\N{\rEng}he puts the patient to sleep and starts the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.37,0:27:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他才刚划下第一刀 党卫军就闯进来...\N{\rEng}He'd just made the first incision when the SS burst in...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.44,0:27:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射杀了躺在病床上的病人 然后射杀罗席嘉医生\N{\rEng}shoot the patient lie on the table then shoot on Dr. Raszeja
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.34,0:27:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着是所有在场的人\N{\rEng}and everybody else who was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.85,0:27:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不是很好笑?\N{\rEng}Isn't that a laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.32,0:27:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那病人浑然不觉 因为他被麻醉了\N{\rEng}The patient didn't feel a thing, he was anesthetized.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.82,0:28:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过别讲扫兴的事 亨瑞\N{\rEng}I said nothing bad.Henryk
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.32,0:28:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了? 都失去幽默感了吗?\N{\rEng}What's the matter with you all? You lost your sense of humor?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.13,0:28:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不好笑\N{\rEng}It's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.93,0:28:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么东西好笑?\N{\rEng}You know what's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.50,0:28:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那条怪里怪气的领带才好笑\N{\rEng}You're funny, with that ridiculous tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.74,0:28:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛讲我的领带? 我的领带招谁惹谁了?\N{\rEng}You talk about my tie for what? What's my tie have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.14,0:28:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上班需要这条领带\N{\rEng}I need this tie for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.67,0:28:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作?\N{\rEng}Your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.37,0:28:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我在工作\N{\rEng}That's right, I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.24,0:28:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 弹钢琴给犹太区的那些寄生虫听\N{\rEng}Yes,your work. Playing the piano for the parasites in the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-寄生虫... -孩子 孩子\N{\rEng}- Parasites... - Boys. Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.91,0:28:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们对人们所受的苦无动于衷...\N{\rEng}They don't give a damn about people some...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.53,0:28:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你因为他们的冷漠谴责我?\N{\rEng}And you blame me for their apathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.88,0:28:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我每天看着这一切\N{\rEng}I do,because I see it everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.65,0:28:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至于对发生在周遭的事情无动于衷\N{\rEng}They don't even notice what's going around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.89,0:28:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要谴责美国人\N{\rEng}I blame the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么? 因为我的领带吗?\N{\rEng}For what? For my tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.42,0:28:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国的犹太人 他们在那里人数不少\N{\rEng}The American Jews, and there are lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.19,0:28:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们对我们做了什么? 他们认为自己在做什么?\N{\rEng}What do they done? What do they think they're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.30,0:28:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人因饥饿而亡\N{\rEng}People here are dying.Haven't got a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.73,0:28:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的犹太银行家应该督促美国对德国宣战\N{\rEng}The Jewish bankers should persuade America to declare war on Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.46,0:29:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关灯 关灯\N{\rEng}The lights! The lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.50,0:29:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.43,0:29:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.02,0:29:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门 我们要进来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.27,0:29:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.04,0:30:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.28,0:30:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.15,0:30:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.51,0:30:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他丢出去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.80,0:30:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.70,0:30:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 我的天\N{\rEng}Oh, please
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.84,0:30:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 我的天\N{\rEng}Oh, my God
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.83,0:30:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我跑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.15,0:31:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我是席皮尔曼先生的姐姐\N{\rEng}Excuse men, I'm Mr. Szpilman's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.63,0:31:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 进去吧 不是你\N{\rEng}Yeah, go in. Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.34,0:32:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-发生什么事? -太可怕了\N{\rEng}- What's up? What's up? - It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.11,0:32:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.19,0:32:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在街上对人群扫射 他们抓走了亨瑞\N{\rEng}They're hunting people in the streets. They've taken Henryk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.95,0:32:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先回家 好吗?\N{\rEng}Go home, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.49,0:32:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先回家 我来处理\N{\rEng}Go home, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.57,0:32:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问一下\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.80,0:32:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看见我丈夫? 伊沙克 沙曼?\N{\rEng}Have you seen my husband? Izaak Szerman?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.57,0:32:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕没有\N{\rEng}Afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.61,0:32:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他高大英俊 蓄着灰色胡子\N{\rEng}Tall, handsome, little gray beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有看见他 请写信通知我\N{\rEng}If you see him, write to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.14,0:32:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记 伊沙克 沙曼\N{\rEng}Don't forget. Izaak Szerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.22,0:33:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生了什么事?\N{\rEng}What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.03,0:33:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们带走了我孙子\N{\rEng}They've got my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.06,0:33:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们逮捕了他\N{\rEng}They pick them up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.23,0:33:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把他带走了\N{\rEng}and take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.23,0:33:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人对他们做了什么\N{\rEng}What do they do to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.46,0:33:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法再继续信仰上帝\N{\rEng}I've stopped believing in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.27,0:33:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 不好意思\N{\rEng}Excuse me. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.84,0:33:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊滋查克\N{\rEng}Itzak?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.21,0:33:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊滋查克 伊滋查克 是我 瓦列 席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Itzak? Itzak, it's Wladek Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.82,0:33:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨瑞在里面\N{\rEng}Henryk is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.25,0:33:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有看见他\N{\rEng}I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.35,0:33:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 他们逮捕了他\N{\rEng}Believe me. They picked him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.92,0:33:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.89,0:33:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮忙吗?\N{\rEng}Can you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.86,0:33:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你需要我了\N{\rEng}Now you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.70,0:33:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 - 现在你需要我了\N{\rEng}- Yes - Now you need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.30,0:33:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮助我们吗?\N{\rEng}Can you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.13,0:33:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有钱就帮\N{\rEng}It costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.27,0:33:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没钱\N{\rEng}I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.70,0:33:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没有我能干的了\N{\rEng}Then there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.24,0:33:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你有机会的时候 你该加入我们\N{\rEng}You should have joined us when you had chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.91,0:33:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊滋查克 他们告诉我你有影响力\N{\rEng}Itzak, They told me you had influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.28,0:33:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁告诉你的?\N{\rEng}Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.41,0:33:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们\N{\rEng}People
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.85,0:34:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的人 他们说你是重要人士\N{\rEng}People I know,They said you're an important man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.25,0:34:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊滋查克...\N{\rEng}Itzak...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.94,0:34:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.11,0:34:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好吗? -强盗 砰  砰 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.31,0:34:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-去死吧 把手举起来 -他是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.83,0:34:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-来一根不 -香烟
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.95,0:34:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感恩不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.17,0:34:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.34,0:34:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去可真无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.67,0:34:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.76,0:34:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.72,0:34:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,举起手来 举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.81,0:35:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万事皆安
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.01,0:35:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊 帮帮我\N{\rEng}Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.25,0:35:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强盗 强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.15,0:35:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.40,0:36:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为何逮捕你?\N{\rEng}Why they picked you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.74,0:36:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去找了伊滋查克 海勒?\N{\rEng}So you go to Itzak Heller?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.97,0:36:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有要你去找他吗?\N{\rEng}Did I ask you to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.18,0:36:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被放出来了 不是吗?\N{\rEng}You're out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.74,0:36:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你求他了吗?\N{\rEng}Did you beg?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.25,0:36:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你对那个人渣卑躬屈膝吗? -不 我请他帮助你\N{\rEng}- Did you bow to that piece of shit? - I asked him to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.28,0:36:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你付给他什么报酬?\N{\rEng}What did you pay him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.42,0:36:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么可以给他? 拿什么?\N{\rEng}With what could I pay him? what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.19,0:36:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赚的每分钱都花在食物上了\N{\rEng}Every zloty I earn were spend on food.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.19,0:36:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以自己解决\N{\rEng}I can look after myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.19,0:36:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把你带走了\N{\rEng}They were taking you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.46,0:36:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那与你一点关系都没有\N{\rEng}It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.56,0:36:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们抓的人是我 不是你\N{\rEng}It's me they wanted, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.56,0:36:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么一定要干涉别人的事情?\N{\rEng}Why do you have to interfere with other people's business?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.10,0:36:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了 这就是你的麻烦 你疯了\N{\rEng}You're mad. That's your trouble. You are mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.24,0:36:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我的事\N{\rEng}That's also my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.51,0:36:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\rEng}hey,what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.08,0:36:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 你病了吗?\N{\rEng}What's the matter? Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.95,0:36:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饿了\N{\rEng}Hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.46,0:37:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就业许可证?\N{\rEng}Employment certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.63,0:37:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思 没有就业许可证会怎样?\N{\rEng}What's that mean, no employment certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.03,0:37:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必需要有就业许可证...\N{\rEng}You have to have an employment certificate...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.57,0:37:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能在犹太区的德属公司工作 否则...\N{\rEng}to work for the Germans firms in the ghetto, otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.84,0:37:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则怎样?\N{\rEng}Otherwise what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.27,0:37:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会被驱逐\N{\rEng}You'll be deported.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.71,0:37:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么谣传是真的了\N{\rEng}So the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.74,0:37:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要重新处置我们...\N{\rEng}They're going to resettle us...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.21,0:37:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我们送到东边的集中营\N{\rEng}and send us to labor camps, in the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.22,0:37:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们要关闭这个小犹太区\N{\rEng}They're closing the small ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.65,0:37:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\N{\rEng}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.57,0:37:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列? 瓦列?\N{\rEng}Wladek? Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.61,0:37:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你会到伦敦 \N{\rEng}I thought you were on tour playing in London,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.96,0:37:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎 纽约 芝加哥巡回演出\N{\rEng} Paris, New York, Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.51,0:37:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个礼拜\N{\rEng}Not this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.44,0:37:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来很糟\N{\rEng}You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.51,0:37:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有听到谣传吗?\N{\rEng}Have you heard the rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.05,0:37:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要把我们重新安置在东部\N{\rEng}They're going to resettle us in the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.88,0:37:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谣传 你太把它们当一回事了\N{\rEng}Rumors! You take it all too much to heart. Wladek
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.62,0:37:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么麻烦吗?\N{\rEng}What's the trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.22,0:38:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直试着帮我父亲申请一张工作许可证\N{\rEng}I've been trying to get the certificate of employment for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.69,0:38:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经设法帮我自己和我其他家人找到了\N{\rEng}I managed to get one for me and the rest of my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.83,0:38:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我还需要另外一张给我父亲\N{\rEng}but I need another one for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.56,0:38:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经跑遍所有公司和商店...\N{\rEng}I've been to all the firms and shops...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.76,0:38:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不来找我呢?\N{\rEng}Why didn't you come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.87,0:38:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在处理许可证的业务\N{\rEng}I didn't know you were in the certificate business.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.93,0:38:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是梅耶克\N{\rEng}I'm not, but Majorek is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.71,0:38:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮忙吗? 但我没钱\N{\rEng}Can you help? I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.81,0:38:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拜托 别贬低我们 -你可以为他做点什么吗?\N{\rEng}- Please, don't insult us. -Can you do something for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.61,0:38:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天四点到修兹工作室\N{\rEng}Be at the Schultz workshop tomorrow, four o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.48,0:38:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你今天运气有多好?\N{\rEng}See what a wonderful piece of luck you've had today?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.38,0:38:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中注定啊\N{\rEng}That's the historical imperative in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.05,0:38:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我常说的 要看光明面\N{\rEng}That's why I always say "Look on the bright side!"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.19,0:38:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光明面 是  我知道\N{\rEng}The bright side,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.94,0:38:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的背怎样了?\N{\rEng}How's your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.41,0:38:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多了\N{\rEng}Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.67,0:38:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多了吗?\N{\rEng}Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.88,0:38:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经好多了\N{\rEng}Better than ask
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.92,0:39:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.59,0:39:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气 虽然我什么忙也帮不上\N{\rEng}My pleasure. Won't help you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.56,0:39:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 修兹先生\N{\rEng}Thank you, Mr. Schultz.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.18,0:39:34.38,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\b1\pos(192,200)\bord0\blur1.2\fad(300,300)\fscx85\fsp0.5}1942年3月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.84,0:40:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我们在犹太区找到工作了\N{\rEng}At least we got work in the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.94,0:40:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我们都还在一起\N{\rEng}At least we are still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.43,0:40:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部出去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.43,0:40:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到院子去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.16,0:40:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别站着不动
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.16,0:40:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是雇员
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.83,0:41:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有工作证
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.30,0:41:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\rEng}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.18,0:41:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.47,0:41:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那里 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.68,0:41:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.32,0:41:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.65,0:41:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.29,0:41:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.66,0:41:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.57,0:41:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其余的人穿好衣服回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.24,0:41:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带着你们的东西 最多15公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.54,0:41:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要把我们送去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.37,0:42:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我已经尽力了\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.21,0:42:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为工作证可以拯救我们\N{\rEng}I thought the certificates'd save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.21,0:42:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 瓦列\N{\rEng}Stop it, Wladek.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.35,0:42:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们一心期望亨瑞和哈琳娜安然无恙\N{\rEng}Let's just hope that Henryk and Halina will be better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.95,0:42:27.75,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\b1\pos(192,200)\bord0\blur1.2\fad(300,300)\fscx85\fsp0.5}1942年8月16日
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.51,0:42:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要到哪里去?\N{\rEng}Where will we be going?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.95,0:42:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去工作\N{\rEng}Going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.25,0:42:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们会比待在那个臭气熏天的犹太区好多了 向前走\N{\rEng}You'll be much better off than in the stinking ghetto. Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.09,0:43:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.42,0:43:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.13,0:43:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.33,0:43:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.73,0:43:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.61,0:43:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.61,0:43:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做? 我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it? Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.65,0:43:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.92,0:43:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.45,0:44:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有水吗?\N{\rEng}Don't you have a bottle of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.48,0:44:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他快死了 我的孩子快要渴死了\N{\rEng}He's dying.My child is dying of thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.42,0:44:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我求求你 求求你 -我很抱歉 \N{\rEng}- I beg you.I beg you. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.39,0:44:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有水吗? 求求你\N{\rEng}Don't you have a bottle of water? I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.72,0:44:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到我说的话吗?\N{\rEng}Did you hear what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.02,0:44:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你 这是一个耻辱\N{\rEng}I'm telling you, it's a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.69,0:44:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在听\N{\rEng}I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.39,0:44:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们任凭他们把我们引向死亡 就像羔羊走向屠场\N{\rEng}Letting them take us to our death like sheep to the slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.90,0:44:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么大声\N{\rEng}Not so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.90,0:44:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们何不反击?\N{\rEng}Why don't we attack them?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.26,0:44:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有五十万人在这里 我们可以突破犹太区重围\N{\rEng}There's half a million of us here. We can break out of the ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.70,0:44:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我们可以光荣地死去 \N{\rEng}At least we can die honorably,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.03,0:44:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是当历史上的一个污点\N{\rEng}not as a stain on the face of History.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.60,0:44:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你这么确定\N{\rEng}Why are you so sure
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.71,0:44:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会送我们下黄泉?\N{\rEng}they're sending us to our death?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.74,0:44:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不确定\N{\rEng}I'm not sure
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.77,0:44:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为什么我不能确定吗?\N{\rEng}You know why I'm not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.84,0:44:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们又没告诉我\N{\rEng}Because they didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.01,0:44:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要把我们赶尽杀绝\N{\rEng}They're going to wipe us all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.75,0:44:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我怎么做? 你要我抗争吗?\N{\rEng}Tell me what do you want me to do? Do you want me to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.05,0:44:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗争的话需要组织 计划 枪支...\N{\rEng}To fight, we need organization, plans, guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.32,0:44:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说得没错 你认为我能做什么\N{\rEng}He's right. Do you think I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.72,0:44:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的小提琴弓抗争吗?\N{\rEng}to fight with my violin bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.42,0:44:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人不会浪费像这样庞大的劳力\N{\rEng}The Germans would never squander a huge labor force like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.92,0:44:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很明显地他们正要把我们送到集中营\N{\rEng}They're sending us to a labor camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.93,0:44:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 当然 看看那个瘸子\N{\rEng}oh,Sure. Look at that cripple there,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.03,0:44:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这些老人跟小孩 他们也要工作吗?\N{\rEng}the old people, the children. They're going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.23,0:44:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你 你要带着背上的铁架一起去吗?\N{\rEng}Look at you. You're going to carry logs on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.11,0:45:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨瑞\N{\rEng}Henryk!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.61,0:45:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈莲娜 亨瑞\N{\rEng}Halina, Henryk!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.45,0:45:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈莲娜 亨瑞\N{\rEng}Halina, Henryk!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.82,0:45:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们听说你们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.26,0:45:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要跟你们在一起\N{\rEng}I wanted to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.17,0:46:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要跟你们在一起\N{\rEng}I wanted to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.34,0:46:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋\N{\rEng}Stupid. Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.51,0:46:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能这样做? 我怎能这样做?\N{\rEng}Why did I do it? Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.25,0:46:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她让我神经紧张\N{\rEng}She's getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.39,0:46:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷 她到底做了什么?\N{\rEng}What did she do, for God's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.12,0:46:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她闷死了她的婴儿\N{\rEng}She smothered her baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.49,0:46:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们准备了一个隐匿处 他们都躲在那里\N{\rEng}They prepared a hiding place and of course they went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.30,0:46:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是当警察来的时候 婴儿哭了起来\N{\rEng}The baby cried just as the police came.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.17,0:46:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她用手捂住啼哭的婴儿\N{\rEng}She smothered the cries with her hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.00,0:46:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婴儿就这么死了\N{\rEng}the baby died.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.71,0:46:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个警察听见了声响\N{\rEng}A policeman heard the death rattle
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.38,0:46:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现他们的藏身之处\N{\rEng}and found where they were hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.72,0:46:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\rEng}mama
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.57,0:47:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在读什么?\N{\rEng}What are you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.37,0:47:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你戳刺我们 我们不会流血吗?\N{\rEng}"If you prick us, de we not bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.68,0:47:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你呵我们痒 我们不会发笑吗?\N{\rEng}If you tickle us, do we not laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.35,0:47:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你对我们下毒 我们不会死去吗?\N{\rEng}If you poison us, do we not die?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.45,0:47:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你加害于我们 我们不应该复仇吗?\N{\rEng}And, if you wrong us,shall we not revenge?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.69,0:47:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写得很好\N{\rEng}Very appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.09,0:47:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这就是我带着它的原因\N{\rEng}Yes. That's why I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.01,0:47:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个傻瓜 他觉得在这里赚钱还有用吗?\N{\rEng}Idiot. What does he think he's gonna do with the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.72,0:47:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 男孩\N{\rEng}Boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.72,0:47:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这里\N{\rEng}come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.26,0:48:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这里\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.26,0:48:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一块奶糖要多少钱?\N{\rEng}How much for a caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.43,0:48:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20波币\N{\rEng}20 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.86,0:48:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 一块奶糖要要这么多?\N{\rEng}What? For one caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.20,0:48:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要怎么花这些钱\N{\rEng}What do you think you're gonna do with the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.93,0:48:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20波币\N{\rEng}20 zlotys.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.93,0:48:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谁有20波币吗?\N{\rEng}We've got 20 between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.34,0:48:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我有10元\N{\rEng}I've got 10, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.68,0:48:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5 10 20\N{\rEng}5, 10, 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.80,0:49:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哈琳娜? -什么?\N{\rEng}- Halina? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.94,0:49:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在说这个挺怪的 但是...\N{\rEng}It's a funny time to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.38,0:49:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.01,0:49:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿我能多了解你一些\N{\rEng}I wish I knew you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.29,0:50:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.64,0:50:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Szpilman
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.64,0:50:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}Szpilman
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.58,0:50:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚开 笨蛋 走
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.15,0:50:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸? 爸爸?\N{\rEng}Papa? Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.29,0:50:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\rEng}papa
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.02,0:50:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈? 哈琳娜?\N{\rEng}Mama? Halina?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.89,0:50:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈琳娜? 妈妈?\N{\rEng}Halina? Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.83,0:50:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己在干嘛 席皮尔曼\N{\rEng}What do you think you're doing,Szpilman?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.56,0:50:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我救了你一命\N{\rEng}I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.60,0:50:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来 快走 走\N{\rEng}Just get up,go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.77,0:50:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别用跑的\N{\rEng}Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.74,0:51:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜 安娜 安娜\N{\rEng}Anna!Anna!Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.80,0:51:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 把他们送去彻底改造
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.13,0:51:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.94,0:51:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个留下 把它给我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.11,0:51:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么? 她是孕妇\N{\rEng}What are you doing? She's pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.25,0:52:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向左转
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.26,0:52:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,齐步走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.73,0:54:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列?\N{\rEng}Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.92,0:54:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里 瓦列?\N{\rEng}Why are you here, Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.12,0:54:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 我  我...\N{\rEng}It's like this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.49,0:54:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们...\N{\rEng}We...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.73,0:54:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们所有人 他们所有人\N{\rEng}All of them, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.13,0:54:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们所有人\N{\rEng}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.40,0:54:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们够幸运 早登极乐\N{\rEng}Perhaps they're lucky. The quicker, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.51,0:54:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没有结束 我们将在这里待上些日子...\N{\rEng}It's not finished yet. We'll stay here for a couple of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.64,0:54:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到尘埃落定\N{\rEng}until things die down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.81,0:54:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经贿赂了一个警察 事情结束的时候他会过来\N{\rEng}I've bribed the policeman, he'll come when it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.53,0:55:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立正 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.29,0:55:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.77,0:55:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 我已经有二年没有出去过了\N{\rEng}My God, I haven't been outside in, it must be two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.14,0:55:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真激动\N{\rEng}Don't get overexcited.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黄金\N{\rEng}gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.89,0:55:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这价钱很好\N{\rEng}Very good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.28,0:56:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有认识的人吗?\N{\rEng}Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.58,0:56:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个美人是谁?\N{\rEng}A beauty. Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.59,0:56:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个歌手 事实上我跟她很熟\N{\rEng}She's a singer. I knew her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.32,0:56:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫是演员\N{\rEng}Her husband is an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.99,0:56:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是好人\N{\rEng}They're good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.63,0:56:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟她说话\N{\rEng}I'd like to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.56,0:56:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记 支援犹太人的都被绞死了\N{\rEng}Don't forget, Wladek.They hang them for helping Jews.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.18,0:56:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向左转
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.76,0:56:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.44,0:56:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.65,0:57:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.55,0:57:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出列
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.80,0:57:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.64,0:57:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.93,0:57:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.73,0:57:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.98,0:57:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.43,0:58:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向右转
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.72,0:58:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.02,0:58:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里待多久了?\N{\rEng}How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.49,0:59:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚开始的\N{\rEng}Since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.83,0:59:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴遇见你\N{\rEng}I was pleased to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.30,0:59:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在即将开始进行最后的安置\N{\rEng}They're going to start the final resettlement now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.47,0:59:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道那意味着什么\N{\rEng}We know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.94,0:59:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们送了一个人出去 席格蒙 他是个好人\N{\rEng}We sent someone out. Zygmund, a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.45,0:59:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他受命追踪从华沙发出的列车\N{\rEng}His orders were to follow the trains out of Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.22,0:59:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他抵达索克洛\N{\rEng}He got to Sokolow.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.52,0:59:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位当地的铁道员告诉他 轨道在那里分歧了\N{\rEng}A man told him the tracks divided,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.43,0:59:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一条通往催布林卡\N{\rEng}one branch's leading to Treblinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.23,0:59:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说每天运货列车载着满车的人从华沙驶来...\N{\rEng}He said everyday freight trains carrying people from Warsaw...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.23,0:59:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开往催布林卡的方向 然后空车返回\N{\rEng}branch off to Treblinka and return empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.40,0:59:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那条路线上 从没看过有食物运送\N{\rEng}No transports of food are ever seen on that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.14,0:59:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而居民被禁止靠近催布林卡车站\N{\rEng}The civilians are forbidden to approach the Treblinka station.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.72,0:59:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在灭绝我们\N{\rEng}They're exterminating us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.89,1:00:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那用不着花太多时间\N{\rEng}It won't take them long.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.89,1:00:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从50万人到现在 我们只剩下6万人\N{\rEng}We are 60 thousand left, out of half a million.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.30,1:00:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎都是年轻人\N{\rEng}Mostly young people.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.20,1:00:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这一次我们要反抗\N{\rEng}And this time we're gonna fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.01,1:00:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们状况良好 组织健全\N{\rEng}We're in good shape.Organized.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.04,1:00:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经准备好了\N{\rEng}We're prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.11,1:00:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你需要援助 我...\N{\rEng}If you need help, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.07,1:00:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 过来\N{\rEng}You! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.54,1:00:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 可恶 可恶\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.72,1:01:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我很抱歉\N{\rEng}sorry.I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.18,1:01:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我刚刚失了神\N{\rEng}I don't know what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.46,1:01:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 拜托 不要 拜托\N{\rEng}please, please
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.63,1:01:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\rEng}please
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.65,1:01:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他拖走
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.20,1:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你弹钢琴的功夫比砌砖好\N{\rEng}I hope you play the piano better than you carry bricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.97,1:02:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会撑太久的 如果他继续这样下去\N{\rEng}He won't last long if he goes on like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.71,1:02:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看我是否能让他好过一点\N{\rEng}I'll see if I can get him something better.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.07,1:02:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有麻烦\N{\rEng}Trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.84,1:02:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集合 只有犹太人\N{\rEng}Round up! Only the Jews.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.11,1:02:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波兰人继续干活 犹太人集合\N{\rEng}The Polish keep working. Only the Jews.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.95,1:02:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有好消息要告诉你们\N{\rEng}I have good news for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.72,1:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都有谣言\N{\rEng}There are rumors going around that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.83,1:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要 呃... \N{\rEng}we like to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.43,1:03:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安置你们\N{\rEng}to resettle you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.03,1:03:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证 从今以后...\N{\rEng}I promise you that now and in the future...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.11,1:03:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也没有新计划\N{\rEng}nothing else is planned.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.84,1:03:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基于这个原因\N{\rEng}For this reason,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.65,1:03:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要在墙上贴公报\N{\rEng}we put information posters on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.45,1:03:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了表示我们的善意...\N{\rEng}To show you our goodwill...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.99,1:03:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该推举你们当中某一个人...\N{\rEng}you should vote one of you to be allowed...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.42,1:03:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他获准每天进城...\N{\rEng}to go in town daily...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.50,1:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带回三公斤的马铃薯...\N{\rEng}and bring 3 kilos of potatoes...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.04,1:03:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一条面包...\N{\rEng}and one loaf of bread
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.40,1:03:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你们每一个工人\N{\rEng}for each of your workers.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.51,1:03:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们要把你们怎么样的话\N{\rEng}So, why should we do something like this
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.34,1:03:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为何还要这样做呢?\N{\rEng}if we'd resettle you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.35,1:03:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以好好做生意...\N{\rEng}You can make good business
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.98,1:03:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做这一行 你们会没饭吃\N{\rEng}out of the things you don't eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.92,1:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是是你们犹太人最擅长的吗?\N{\rEng}Isn't that something that you Jews are good in?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.02,1:04:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赚钱?\N{\rEng}Making money?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.90,1:04:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.35,1:04:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...是用绳子绑的\N{\rEng}That one, with the string.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.48,1:04:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它的用铁线绑\N{\rEng}The others, tied by wire.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.02,1:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在\N{\rEng}Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.26,1:06:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅耶克\N{\rEng}Majorek.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.00,1:06:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你帮我一个忙\N{\rEng}I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.37,1:06:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要离开这里\N{\rEng}I want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.77,1:06:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出去很容易\N{\rEng}It's easy to get out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.31,1:06:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,困难的是你要如何在外面存活下来\N{\rEng}It's how you survive on the other side,that's hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.31,1:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 我明白\N{\rEng}I know.I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.31,1:06:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天\N{\rEng}Last summer,I worked for a day
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.18,1:06:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾在兹兰那 布拉马广场工作了一天\N{\rEng}in the Zelazna Brama Square.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.65,1:06:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见一个认识的人 她是个老朋友了\N{\rEng}I saw someone I knew, she's an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.15,1:06:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位歌手 她丈夫是个演员\N{\rEng}A singer, her husband is an actor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.26,1:06:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我写下他们的名字跟地址\N{\rEng}I've filled their names down and their address,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.76,1:06:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们还住在原处的话\N{\rEng}if they're still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.50,1:06:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉琳娜 果朵瓦丝卡和安德兹 博克基\N{\rEng}Janina Godlewska and Andrzej Bogucki.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.50,1:06:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是好人\N{\rEng}They're good people.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.03,1:06:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能试着连络上他们吗?\N{\rEng}Would you try to make contact?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.47,1:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都进城 你能问问他们...\N{\rEng}You go to town everyday, would you just ask them...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.78,1:07:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问他们是否能帮我逃离这里\N{\rEng}Ask them if they'd help me get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.24,1:07:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有药膏吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.12,1:07:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上来做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.19,1:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面是什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.86,1:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们获准把食物带进犹太区
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.03,1:08:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3公斤的马铃薯和面包
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.07,1:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.44,1:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马铃薯和面包
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.61,1:08:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谎 我嗅到你的谎言了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.24,1:08:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.58,1:08:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马铃薯?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.35,1:08:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们犹太人都一样
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.29,1:09:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们犹太人...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.16,1:09:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...总是
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.09,1:09:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.58,1:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再骗我 我就把你给毙了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.35,1:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以名义起誓
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.27,1:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试着去找你的朋友\N{\rEng}I tried your friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.44,1:09:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有住在那里了\N{\rEng}They don't live there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.74,1:09:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...你联络到了吗?\N{\rEng}Did you make contact?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.91,1:09:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以准备离开了\N{\rEng}Be ready to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.28,1:09:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何时?\N{\rEng}When?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.18,1:09:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快\N{\rEng}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.05,1:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立定\N{\rEng}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.88,1:10:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.87,1:10:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我教你们什么叫纪律 犹太猪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.21,1:10:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么要扁你们吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.71,1:10:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不 -知道为什么要扁你们吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.05,1:10:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.28,1:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了庆祝耶诞夜
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.95,1:10:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 前进
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.35,1:10:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进 把歌唱起来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.46,1:10:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱点让人振奋的歌
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.06,1:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大声地唱 整齐地唱
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.08,1:11:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.90,1:13:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我脏兮兮的\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. I'm dirty. I'm so filthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.66,1:13:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有太多时间 来吧\N{\rEng}We haven't much time.Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.07,1:13:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得快一点\N{\rEng}We must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.21,1:13:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里 看看合不合身\N{\rEng}Here. See if this fit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.08,1:13:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得一直换地方\N{\rEng}We have to keep moving
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.38,1:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人现在不分青红皂白地搜捕\N{\rEng}Germans are hunting down indiscriminately now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.98,1:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹太人 非犹太人 任何人 每一个人\N{\rEng}Jews, non-Jews, anybody, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.42,1:13:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列 你最好刮一下胡子\N{\rEng}Wladek, You better shave.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.85,1:13:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我架子上的刮胡刀\N{\rEng}Use my razor on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.60,1:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马里克 吉勃克辛斯基会照顾你的\N{\rEng}You'll be looked after by Gebczynski.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.54,1:14:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住在城的另一边\N{\rEng}He's on the other side of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.84,1:14:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你就待在那里 我们会再帮你找新的住处\N{\rEng}You stay there tonight, then we'll find you somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.35,1:14:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会带食物给你\N{\rEng}I'll bring you food.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.72,1:14:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我们走了\N{\rEng}Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.96,1:15:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉你要睡在哪里\N{\rEng}I'll show you where you're going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.36,1:15:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必需在这边待到明天下午\N{\rEng}You have to stay here until tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.49,1:15:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在犹太区围墙附近为你准备了公寓\N{\rEng}We have a flat for you near the ghetto wall.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.93,1:15:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那里很安全\N{\rEng}But it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.67,1:15:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不太舒适\N{\rEng}It's not going to be very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.68,1:16:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经很好了\N{\rEng}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.39,1:16:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.37,1:16:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿 给我 \N{\rEng}Here. Here. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.74,1:16:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅可能往前坐 靠近德国区 \N{\rEng}Go as near to the front as possible, to the German section.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.90,1:16:56.69,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,请勿穿过
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.93,1:17:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要拉下窗帘 \N{\rEng}I'm going to draw the curtains now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.94,1:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你整个白天要任由它们敞开着 \N{\rEng}But you leave them open during the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.94,1:17:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记 \N{\rEng}Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.58,1:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在墙的这一边一定会好过些吧\N{\rEng}Must feel better on this side of the wall,eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.02,1:17:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 \N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.02,1:17:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有时候我仍不确定自己是在墙的哪一边 \N{\rEng}But sometimes I'm still not sure which side of the wall I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.36,1:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有些面包... 马铃薯 洋葱 \N{\rEng}Some bread, potatoes, onions.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.16,1:18:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再来的 \N{\rEng}I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.46,1:18:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有妮娜 博嘉琪 每周会来看你二次 \N{\rEng}Janina will visit you twice a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.83,1:18:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你带更多食物 看看你好不好 \N{\rEng}bring more food, see how you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.70,1:18:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 \N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.84,1:18:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个非常重要 \N{\rEng}This is very important.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.14,1:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果万一发生紧急状况... 我是说非常紧急\N{\rEng}In case of emergency...I mean emergency,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.55,1:18:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这个地址去 \N{\rEng}go to this address.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.52,1:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你说忘记是什么意思?\N{\rEng}Fuck you dog, what do you mean you forgot?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.96,1:19:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我是什么意思?\N{\rEng}What do you think I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.79,1:19:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思就是我忘记了 \N{\rEng}I forgot, that's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.23,1:19:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你待我如粪土\N{\rEng}You know what, you treat me like dirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.50,1:19:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我待你如粪土? 因为你就是粪土 \N{\rEng}Treat you like dirt? Because you are a dirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.70,1:19:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猪头 猪头 \N{\rEng}Pig! Pig!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.00,1:19:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-婊子 - 你是只肮脏的猪猡\N{\rEng}- Bitch! - You are a dirty pig!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.44,1:19:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此 猪头 \N{\rEng}Takes one to know one. Pig.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.51,1:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你弹琴时像个天使 \N{\rEng}Um,you play like an angel, Catskin.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.78,1:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我弹琴像个天使 你为什么不听?\N{\rEng}If I look like an angel, why don't you listen?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.39,1:19:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有听啊 小喵咪 \N{\rEng}I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.82,1:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗子 你明明睡着了 小猪头 \N{\rEng}Liar. You fell asleep. Pig.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.53,1:19:47.33,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\b1\pos(192,200)\bord0\blur1.2\fad(300,300)\fscx85\fsp0.5}1943年4月19日
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.54,1:20:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散开 我们遭到袭击了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.09,1:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏起来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.18,1:20:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.27,1:20:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隐蔽 开火
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.32,1:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 跑呀
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.87,1:20:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击 射击 \N{\rEng}fire!fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.77,1:22:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷袭成功
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.18,1:22:02.38,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\b1\pos(192,200)\bord0\blur1.2\fad(300,300)\fscx85\fsp0.5}1943年5月16日
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.18,1:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那栋楼...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.97,1:22:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转过去
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.42,1:22:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.65,1:22:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 \N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.72,1:22:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我本想早点来的 但... -不 谢谢你 \N{\rEng}- I wanted to come earlier, but... - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.03,1:23:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人想到会他们会坚持这么久 \N{\rEng}No one thought they'd hold out so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.10,1:23:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不应该出来的 \N{\rEng}I never should've come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.47,1:23:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该留在那里 与他们一起战斗 \N{\rEng}I should have stayed and fought with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.70,1:23:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列 别那么说\N{\rEng}Wladyslaw, stop that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.64,1:23:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在都结束了 \N{\rEng}It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.41,1:23:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该为他们感到骄傲 \N{\rEng}Just be proud of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.51,1:23:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 他们发起了抗争?\N{\rEng}My God, did they put up a fight?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.88,1:23:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 \N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.11,1:23:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人发动了战斗\N{\rEng}So did the Germans.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.52,1:23:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们非常震惊 \N{\rEng}They were in shock!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.12,1:23:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有预料到 没有人预料得到 \N{\rEng}They didn't expect it. Nobody expected it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.25,1:23:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹太人反击了 \N{\rEng}Jews fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.06,1:23:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会想到呢?\N{\rEng}Who would thought?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.96,1:23:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做有什么好处呢?\N{\rEng}What good did it do?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.76,1:23:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么好处?\N{\rEng}What good?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.06,1:23:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列 你真让我吃惊 \N{\rEng}Wladek, I'm surprised with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.87,1:23:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们尊严地死去 这就是好处 \N{\rEng}They died with dignity.That what good they did.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.54,1:23:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还知道别的吗?\N{\rEng}And you know something else?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.57,1:23:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在波兰人要反抗 \N{\rEng}Now the Poles will rise.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.94,1:23:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们准备好了 \N{\rEng}We are ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.88,1:23:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要抗争 你知道吗?\N{\rEng}We'll fight too. You see.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.19,1:24:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的东西收拾好 你必需离开 \N{\rEng}Get your things together. You have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.80,1:24:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 发生什么事了?\N{\rEng}What? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.80,1:24:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要逃亡了 \N{\rEng}I'm on the run.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.14,1:24:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?\N{\rEng}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.14,1:24:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密警察发现我们的武器了 \N{\rEng}The Gestapo found our weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.14,1:24:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经逮捕了嘉琳娜和安德兹 \N{\rEng}They've arrested Janina and Andrzej.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.34,1:24:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也将要查出这个地方 \N{\rEng}They're bound to find out about this place too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.13,1:24:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必需马上离开 \N{\rEng} You must get away at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.57,1:24:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我到哪里去?\N{\rEng}Where do you want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.05,1:24:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我\N{\rEng}Look at me,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.41,1:24:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不走 \N{\rEng}I'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.54,1:24:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能在这里碰碰运气吗?\N{\rEng}Can I take my chances here?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.87,1:24:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的决定 \N{\rEng}That's your decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.18,1:24:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是当他们突击公寓的时候 从窗户跳出去...\N{\rEng}But when they storm the flat, throw yourself out the window...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.99,1:24:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们活捉你 \N{\rEng}don't let them get you alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.68,1:24:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身上有毒药  他们也不可能活捉我 \N{\rEng}I have poison on me. They won't get me alive either.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.90,1:28:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\N{\rEng}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.29,1:28:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上开门 不然我们要叫警察来了 \N{\rEng}Open the door or we'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.14,1:28:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这栋公寓的人吗?\N{\rEng}Are you from this flat?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.42,1:28:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有登记 \N{\rEng}You're not registered.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.16,1:28:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我朋友的房子 \N{\rEng}It belongs to a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.74,1:28:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来拜访他  但他不在家 \N{\rEng}I just came to visit, but not, I just missed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.04,1:28:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有身份证吗? \N{\rEng}Have you got your identity card?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.60,1:28:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看你的身份证\N{\rEng}Let me see your identity card.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.77,1:28:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEng}Yes,of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.61,1:28:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要看你的身份证\N{\rEng}I want to see your identity card!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.18,1:28:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\rEng}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.06,1:29:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是犹太人 犹太人 拦住这个犹太人 \N{\rEng}He's a Jew! A Jew! Stop the Jew!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.40,1:29:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他出去 拦住他\N{\rEng}Don't let him out! Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.28,1:30:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁?\N{\rEng}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.85,1:30:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉勃克辛斯基先生要我来的 \N{\rEng}Mr. Gebczynski sent me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.75,1:30:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列迪斯洛 席皮尔曼 \N{\rEng}Wladyslaw Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.53,1:30:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多萝塔 \N{\rEng}Dorota.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.74,1:30:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来 \N{\rEng}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.69,1:30:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我...\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.I...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.53,1:30:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有人给我这个地址 \N{\rEng}I'm sorry. I was given this address.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.34,1:30:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来找一位德兹奇威兹先生 \N{\rEng}and I'm looking for a Mr. Dzikiewicz.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.62,1:30:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克 德兹奇威兹 他是我的丈夫 \N{\rEng}Michael Dzikiewicz, he's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.92,1:30:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来 \N{\rEng}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.91,1:31:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐 \N{\rEng}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.19,1:31:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要帮助 \N{\rEng}I need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.10,1:31:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会在宵禁之前回来 \N{\rEng}He'll be back before curfew.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.06,1:31:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在躲藏 \N{\rEng}I've been in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.66,1:31:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一个藏身之处 \N{\rEng}I need somewhere to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.13,1:31:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就快回来了 \N{\rEng}Be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.97,1:31:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你结婚多久了?\N{\rEng}How long have you been married?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.00,1:31:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才满一年 \N{\rEng}Just over a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.14,1:31:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘瑞克怎么样了?\N{\rEng}And how is Jurek?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.81,1:31:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了 \N{\rEng}Dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.25,1:31:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的宝宝什么时候出世?\N{\rEng}When is your baby due?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.39,1:31:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节 \N{\rEng}Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.69,1:31:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是养育小孩的好时机 但当时... \N{\rEng}This is not a good time to have children, but then...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.89,1:31:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我先生 这是瓦列迪斯洛 席皮尔曼 \N{\rEng}This is my husband. Wladyslaw Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.56,1:31:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马里克 吉勃克辛斯基要他来的 \N{\rEng}Marek Gebczynski sent him.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.10,1:31:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我记得\N{\rEng}Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.17,1:32:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉勃克辛斯基说过只有在紧急时才来找你 \N{\rEng}Mr. Gebczynski said to contact you only in case of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.94,1:32:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不用担心了 \N{\rEng}Don't worry now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.85,1:32:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我们不能把你送走 你就睡在沙发 \N{\rEng}We can't move you tonight. You'll sleep on the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.89,1:32:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 \N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.47,1:32:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我可以吃片面包吗?\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, could I have a piece of bread?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.67,1:32:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我们一起吃 \N{\rEng}Yes, of course. We will eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.17,1:32:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐 请坐 \N{\rEng}Sit. Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.01,1:32:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 \N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.57,1:34:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在正置身德国区 \N{\rEng}You're on a very German area.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.84,1:34:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对面的建筑物是一家医院 \N{\rEng}Building on the opposite is a hospital
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.84,1:34:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收容从俄国前线回来的伤兵 \N{\rEng}taking wounded from the Russian front.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.08,1:35:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它隔壁就是纳粹党卫军\N{\rEng}And next door is the Schutzpolizei.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.85,1:35:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最安全的地方 \N{\rEng}Safest place to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.26,1:35:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在狮子巢穴的正中心 \N{\rEng}Right at the heart of the lion's den.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.40,1:35:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你锁在里面 \N{\rEng}I'll be locking you in.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.80,1:35:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人知道你在这里 所以尽可能保持安静 \N{\rEng}No one knows you're here,so keep as quiet as possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.17,1:37:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧?\N{\rEng}All well?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.94,1:37:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 \N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.44,1:37:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是安提克 札勒斯 \N{\rEng}This is Antek Szalas.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.48,1:37:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他将会照顾你 \N{\rEng}He'll be looking after you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.48,1:37:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好? -你好 ?\N{\rEng}- How do you do? - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.52,1:37:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 \N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.45,1:37:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经给了他一把备用钥匙\N{\rEng}I've given him a second key.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.89,1:37:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会带食物给你 看你是否安然无恙 \N{\rEng}He'll bring food,see that you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.99,1:37:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是地下组织成员 人很好\N{\rEng}He's with the underground,he's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.66,1:38:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得我了 席皮尔曼先生 \N{\rEng}You don't remember me?Mr Szpilman.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.60,1:38:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不记得了 \N{\rEng}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.27,1:38:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华沙广播电台 我是一个技术人员 \N{\rEng}Warsaw Radio. I was a technician.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.10,1:38:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我几乎每天都看见你 \N{\rEng}I saw you almost everyday.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.84,1:38:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不记得了 我...\N{\rEng}I'm sorry,I don't remember.I...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.58,1:38:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系 \N{\rEng}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.55,1:38:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心任何事情 我会常来看你的\N{\rEng}You've nothing to worry about. I'll visit often.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.22,1:38:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会很高兴听到联军正在轰炸德国... \N{\rEng}You'll be pleased to hear that the Allies are bombing Germany...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.79,1:38:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜复一夜 夜复一夜\N{\rEng}night after night,after night.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.32,1:38:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科隆 汉堡 柏林 \N{\rEng}Cologne,Hamburg,Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.69,1:38:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而俄国人将会真正把他们带入地狱 \N{\rEng}And the Russians are really giving them hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.00,1:38:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是终结的开始 \N{\rEng}It's the beginning of the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.36,1:38:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此 \N{\rEng}Oh,Let's hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.76,1:38:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.14,1:38:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.27,1:38:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个 小心点
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.04,1:39:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗?\N{\rEng}Still alive then?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.22,1:39:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有香肠 面包 \N{\rEng}Here. Sausage,bread.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.52,1:39:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那瓶伏特加还没喝完吗?\N{\rEng}You still got that vodka?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.84,1:39:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还得持续多久呢?\N{\rEng}How long is this meant to last?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.31,1:39:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久了 \N{\rEng}Not long now.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.74,1:39:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我想...我得了黄疸\N{\rEng}I thin…think I've got jaundice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.08,1:39:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心那个 \N{\rEng}You don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.95,1:40:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它只是让你看起来比较好笑\N{\rEng}Just makes you look funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.12,1:40:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爷爷当年出黄疸时被他女朋友甩了 \N{\rEng}My grandfather was jilted by his girlfriend when he got jaundice.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.32,1:40:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝光它 \N{\rEng}Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.09,1:40:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为...为什么你不早一点来?\N{\rEng}Why...why didn't you come sooner?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.76,1:40:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经超过二个礼拜了 \N{\rEng}It's been over two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.23,1:40:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么问题了吗? \N{\rEng}Problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.26,1:40:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱 \N{\rEng}Money.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.80,1:40:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必需筹钱买食物 \N{\rEng}I've got to raise money to buy the food.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.70,1:40:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要可以卖的东西 \N{\rEng}I need things to sell,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.34,1:40:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不容易 \N{\rEng}it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.21,1:40:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 把它卖了\N{\rEng}Here. Sell this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.41,1:40:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,食物比时间重要 \N{\rEng}Food is more important than time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.09,1:40:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我要告诉你 \N{\rEng}Oh,yes. I meant to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.46,1:40:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联军已经在法国登陆了\N{\rEng}The Allies have landed in France.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.19,1:40:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄国军队就快要到这里了\N{\rEng}Russians will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.93,1:40:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会把狗娘养的德国人赶走... \N{\rEng}They'll beat the shit out of the Germans...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.73,1:40:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可能到 \N{\rEng}any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.84,1:41:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不  不 \N{\rEng}No No No
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.74,1:41:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列\N{\rEng}Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.32,1:41:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦列 \N{\rEng}Wladek?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.42,1:41:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道 我就知道这会发生 \N{\rEng}I knew it.I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.36,1:41:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要去找医生 -你不能去 这样太危险了 \N{\rEng}- I'll get a doctor - You can't. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.66,1:41:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找路札克医生 我们可以信任他 \N{\rEng}Dr. Luczak. We can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.50,1:41:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多萝塔 别傻了 他是儿科医生\N{\rEng}Ridiculous.Don't be stupid.He's a pediatrician.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.73,1:41:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也是医生\N{\rEng}He's still a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.90,1:42:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你留下 我去找\N{\rEng}No.You stay. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.74,1:42:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来道别的 \N{\rEng}We came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.84,1:42:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要到奥特沃茨克跟我妈妈在一起 \N{\rEng}We're going to stay with my mother in Otwocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.98,1:42:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝宝已经在那里了 那里更安全 \N{\rEng}The baby is already there.It's safer.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.48,1:42:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说暴动随时都有可能开始 \N{\rEng}There's talk that the uprising will begin any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.89,1:42:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,札勒斯可能被射杀了 \N{\rEng}That man Szalas should be shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.52,1:43:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为了你在华沙到处募款 \N{\rEng}He's been collecting money on your behalf all over Warsaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.53,1:43:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显然人们慷慨解囊 \N{\rEng}Apparently people gave generously,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.50,1:43:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他筹到了一笔可观的数目 \N{\rEng}so he collected a tidy sum.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.70,1:43:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 \N{\rEng}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.81,1:43:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肝脏肿得像颗橄榄球 \N{\rEng}The liver the size of a football.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.78,1:43:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胆囊有严重的发炎 ...\N{\rEng}Inflammation of the gall bladder...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.75,1:43:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他会活着 \N{\rEng}but he'll live.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.32,1:43:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会试着给他找些果糖 \N{\rEng}I'll try to get him some laevulose,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.66,1:43:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这并不容易 \N{\rEng}but it's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.86,1:43:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以再来看他吗?\N{\rEng}Can you visit him again?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.26,1:43:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不确定\N{\rEng}Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.46,1:43:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生?\N{\rEng}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.63,1:43:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢你 -别说话 休息 \N{\rEng}- thank you. - Don't speak,rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.44,1:43:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感激你过来 \N{\rEng}Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.68,1:43:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们给你带来一些食物 \N{\rEng}We brought you some food.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.11,1:43:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要为你准备些东西\N{\rEng}I'll prepare something now for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.98,1:43:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们就得走了 \N{\rEng}then we must go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.45,1:44:02.12,Screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\b1\pos(192,200)\bord0\blur1.2\fad(0,300)\fscx85\fsp0.5}1944年8月1日
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.91,1:44:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有个受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.96,1:44:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.63,1:44:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当心点 当心点
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.17,1:44:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我去找人帮忙 -快点
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.80,1:45:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧 把担架抬过来
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.64,1:45:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退到里边去
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.40,1:46:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去\N{\rEng}get out
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.33,1:47:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去 出去 快到街上去\N{\rEng}get out!get out!get out the street!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.47,1:47:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到街上去\N{\rEng}get out the street!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.60,1:47:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在出去 德国人已经把这栋楼给包围了\N{\rEng}Get out now! The Germans have surrounded the building!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.35,1:47:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊 来人啊 快来人帮我\N{\rEng}Somebody...Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.28,1:48:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗? 这里太脏了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.83,1:48:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来检查这边 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.62,1:48:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细点
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.51,1:49:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-亨里齐 -我正在检查
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.72,1:49:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.35,1:49:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-快下来 -好的 这就下来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.69,1:53:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 把他们都堆在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.86,1:53:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扔过去
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.32,1:55:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把所有的东西都做上标记
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.33,1:55:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.58,2:02:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.18,2:02:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.62,2:02:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听的懂吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.29,2:02:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.66,2:02:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.70,2:02:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.67,2:02:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试着要把罐头打开
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.51,2:02:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你住在这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:47.65,2:02:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里工作吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.82,2:02:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,2:02:55.22,2:02:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的职业是什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.09,2:03:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.10,2:03:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是钢琴师
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.14,2:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴师
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.22,2:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.15,2:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹吧
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.04,2:09:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你躲在这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.68,2:09:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹太人?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.12,2:09:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你躲在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.42,2:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阁楼
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.69,2:09:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我去看
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.35,2:10:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有吃的吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.98,2:10:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说 这非常的重要...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.45,2:11:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立正
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.88,2:11:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.85,2:11:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安上校
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.25,2:12:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹太人
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.60,2:12:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请问...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.50,2:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些炮火是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:39.07,2:12:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄国人正要渡河
Dialogue: 0,2:12:43.14,2:12:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需再等两个礼拜就够了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:17.70,2:14:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.07,2:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要撤退了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:23.78,2:14:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄国人来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.61,2:14:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.08,2:14:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么感谢你
Dialogue: 0,2:14:35.46,2:14:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢上帝 不用谢我
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.09,2:14:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他让我们死里逃生
Dialogue: 0,2:14:40.23,2:14:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么我们要信仰他
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.27,2:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你 拿着
Dialogue: 0,2:14:57.98,2:14:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.11,2:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一件
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.31,2:15:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件更暖和
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.65,2:15:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束后你要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.02,2:15:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续在波兰电台
Dialogue: 0,2:15:15.29,2:15:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弹钢琴
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.33,2:15:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.17,2:15:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我会来听你演奏
Dialogue: 0,2:15:22.10,2:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席皮尔曼
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.54,2:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席皮尔曼
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.51,2:15:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对钢琴师来说这是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.76,2:16:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德国人 德国人\N{\rEng}German! German!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.48,2:17:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要开枪 我是波兰人\N{\rEng}Don't shoot, I'm Polish!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.02,2:17:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是波兰人\N{\rEng}I'm Polish!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:25.56,2:17:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来 举起双手\N{\rEng}Come out with your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.43,2:17:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 我求求你\N{\rEng}Please! I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.43,2:17:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要开枪 不要开枪 我求求你\N{\rEng}Don't shoot, don't shoot.I beg you,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:32.90,2:17:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是波兰人\N{\rEng}I'm a Polish.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:34.20,2:17:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下来\N{\rEng}Come down!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:40.04,2:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 我是波兰人 拜托\N{\rEng}Please, I'm Polish.Please
Dialogue: 0,2:17:43.24,2:17:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 他是波兰人\N{\rEng}Please.He's Polish.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:49.32,2:17:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他是波兰人\N{\rEng}Yes, he's Polish.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:52.75,2:17:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件该死的外套是怎么回事?\N{\rEng}Why the fucking coat?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.36,2:17:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很冷\N{\rEng}I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.61,2:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他们 婊子养的德国人\N{\rEng}Look at them.German fuckers!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:21.11,2:18:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶手 凶手\N{\rEng}Murderers! Murderers!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.32,2:18:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肮脏的狗杂种\N{\rEng}Dirty bastards!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:26.89,2:18:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人魔 杂种\N{\rEng}Assassins! Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.49,2:18:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你们现在 你们夺走了我的一切\N{\rEng}Look at you now! You took everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:33.73,2:18:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个音乐家 你们夺走了我的小提琴\N{\rEng}Me, a musician.You took my violin,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.83,2:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗娘养的 你们夺走我的灵魂\N{\rEng}you took my soul.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:43.74,2:18:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音乐家?\N{\rEng}Musician?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:46.84,2:18:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是音乐家?\N{\rEng}Are you a musician?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.94,2:18:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\rEng}yeah
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.71,2:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你认识...\N{\rEng}Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.08,2:18:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴家席皮尔曼吗?\N{\rEng}a pianist called Szpilman,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.45,2:18:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是为波兰电台演奏的?\N{\rEng}from the Polish radio station?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:55.68,2:18:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然认识他\N{\rEng}Of course I know him.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.92,2:19:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在避难时 我帮助过他\N{\rEng}I helped him to hide himself.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:01.52,2:19:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他我在这里\N{\rEng}Tell him I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:04.09,2:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请他帮助我\N{\rEng}Ask him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.66,2:19:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你叫什么名字? -霍森菲尔\N{\rEng}- What's your name? - Hosenfeld.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:12.60,2:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:56.47,2:20:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里 我很确定\N{\rEng}It was here, I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.07,2:21:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在已经不在了\N{\rEng}Well, it's not here now.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:03.44,2:21:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对着他们咆哮\N{\rEng}I shouted, abused them.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:05.08,2:21:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在一点也不觉得骄傲 但我当时就是那样做的\N{\rEng}I'm not proud of it, but that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:07.85,2:21:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当年就站在你现在这个位置\N{\rEng}I stood where you are now.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.18,2:21:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里围着有刺的铁丝网\N{\rEng}There was a barbed wire
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.58,2:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个德国军官向我走来\N{\rEng}and this German came up to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.09,2:21:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听到他的名字吗?\N{\rEng}You didn't catch his name?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:16.86,2:21:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.93,2:21:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去那间工厂问问 也许他们知道些什么\N{\rEng}I'll ask at the factory.They may know something.
